comments.body:
@kevinreiss and I discussed yesterday to keep the UI so that we can display what locations exist but to remove any actions that allow to edit, update, create or delete any location or library through the UI https://github.com/pulibrary/bibdata/issues/1193. 
Also support the locations and libraries updates through json files that will exist in the code base. 

For any potential change we should update the files and with a rake task we would update production or development. This discussion happened so that I can proceed with https://github.com/pulibrary/bibdata/issues/1103
